<simplesect kind="version"><para>0.8.0</para>
</simplesect>
The Content Control Identifier (CCID) API manages CCIDs for <ref refid="group__bt__uuid_1gab76981ff7b5fe1949c606e901daa33d3" kindref="member">BT_UUID_CCID</ref> characteristics. </para>
